data.description: Two lots available together or separately! Close proximity to Beaver Lake! Great potential spot for your lake home, or possibly a couple of Vacation Rentals. Home on property is considered of no value. Property is being sold As Is. Some utilities are available, or already on property. Warning! Property has had lots of debris removed, which has left lots of broken glass and sharp objects. Wear proper protection and enter at own risk.
